scoringPlays.text: Giles Jackson 97 Yd Kickoff Return (Jake Moody Kick)
Zach Charbonnet 2 Yd Run (Jake Moody Kick)
Zach Charbonnet 8 Yd Run (Jake Moody Kick)
Nick Eubanks 5 Yd pass from Shea Patterson (Quinn Nordin Kick)
Hassan Haskins 14 Yd Run (Quinn Nordin Kick)
Javon Leake 97 Yd Kickoff Return (Joseph Petrino Kick)

videos.description: Giles Jackson returns the opening kickoff 97 yards for a Michigan touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan takes opening kickoff 97 yards to the house) 2019/11/2

videos.headline: Michigan takes opening kickoff 97 yards to the house

videos.description: Michigan RB Zach Charbonnet takes the direct snap and pushes across the goal line for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Charbonnet adds to Michigan’s lead with short TD) 2019/11/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Charbonnet adds to Michigan's lead with short TD

videos.description: Michigan spoils the Maryland drive as Josh Metellus leaps and grabs the interception after Maryland's Jackson is hit as he's throwing.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Maryland’s Jackson gets hit while throwing and is picked off) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Maryland's Jackson gets hit while throwing and is picked off

videos.description: On fourth-and-one, Michigan decides to run a fake punt and picks up 14 yards for the first down.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Michigan runs a fake punt for a 1st down) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Michigan runs a fake punt for a 1st down

videos.description: Shea Patterson goes deep to Nico Collins for 51 yards, and Zach Charbonnet finds the end zone a couple of plays later from eight yards out.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patterson's long pass to Collins sets up a Michigan TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Patterson's long pass to Collins sets up a Michigan TD

videos.description: Shea Patterson fakes the handoff then finds a wide-open Nick Eubanks for a 5-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Patterson finds Eubanks for the easy TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Patterson finds Eubanks for the easy TD

videos.description: Maryland's Javon Leake takes the kickoff and goes 97 yards to the house for the game's second 97-yard kickoff return touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Leake goes 97 yards for the kickoff return TD) 2019/11/02

videos.headline: Leake goes 97 yards for the kickoff return TD

videos.description: Michigan starts the game with a 97-yard kickoff return for a touchdown, and Zach Charbonnet runs in two touchdowns as the Wolverines beat Maryland 38-7.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Michigan dominates Maryland 38-7) 2019/11/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Michigan dominates Maryland 38-7
